article.headline: Smith leads Grambling to 69-60 victory over Bethune-Cookman
article.description: — Jourdan Smith had 17 points in Grambling's 69-60 victory over Bethune-Cookman on Monday night.
article.linkText: Smith leads Grambling to 69-60 victory over Bethune-Cookman
article.story: GRAMBLING, La. -- — Jourdan Smith had 17 points in Grambling's 69-60 victory over Bethune-Cookman on Monday night. Smith also had five rebounds for the Tigers (16-13, 13-3 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Tra'Michael Moton scored 14 with three steals. Jalen Johnson added 11 points. Dhashon Dyson led the way for the Wildcats (15-15, 10-7) with 15 points. Seneca Willoughby added 14 points, six rebounds and two steals. Jakobi Heady had 12 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
